js
Copy
Edit
const dq = new Deque();
dq.addBack("A");
dq.addBack("B");
dq.addFront("C");
dq.removeBack(); // Removes B
console.log(dq.peekFront()); // C
console.log(dq.peekBack());  // A
Flexibility is power ğŸ’ª â€” and Deque gives us just that!

